                <p>This project is an interactive Pokedex that allows users to explore Pokémon from the first to the seventh generation, encompassing a total of approximately 800 Pokémon.</p>
                <p>The information for each Pokémon has been extracted from a CSV database and organized into different tables for easier management and access.</p>
                <p>The Pokedex includes features such as:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Searching by name</li>
                    <li>Filtering by type and generation</li>
                    <li>Viewing individual details for each Pokémon</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Additionally, a modern design has been implemented using Bulma CSS, providing a user-friendly and visually appealing experience.</p>
                <p>This project is perfect for Pokémon enthusiasts and anyone looking to learn more about each creature and its characteristics.</p>
